{
  "design_notes": "Designed an easy chart focusing on steady quarter-note rhythms with comfortable, logical flow. Utilized 0.5-beat holds to construct a fun 'hold roll' sequence during the climax (bar 50-51 and 54-55) to elevate the energy without exceeding the 3.0 NPS limit or the 20% hold share. Ensured a highly sparse breather section in S4 to reflect the drop in song energy.",
